$ Oracle: Statistics gathering

There are several methods to gather → development/databases/Oracle/optimizer/statistics:
table { ll
  Automatic ☰
  Manual ☰
  → development/databases/Oracle/optimizer/statistics/gathering/online[Online] ☰
  → development/databases/Oracle/optimizer/statistics/gathering/real-time[Real-time] ☰
  High frequency autoomatic ☰
table }

sa:

  The `gather*` procedures of the `→ development/databases/Oracle/installed/packages/dbms/stats` package.
  
  The `gather_plan_statistics` → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/hints.

  → development/databases/Oracle/installed/data-dictionary/base-tables/col_usage[`sys.col_usage$`]
